    "description": "Ceaseless Night is a strategic roguelike that captures the essence of dungeon crawling in a bleak world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gather Your Party</h2>Whether through finding adventurers in the dungeons or stumbling upon those that wander into camp, you must assemble a party of up to 4 heroes to fight in hopes of reclaiming the light. Discover new trinkets, Slay monsters ranging from rats, to oozes, to dragons. Survive using your wit, skill, and a bit of luck.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Core Of the Game</h2></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>19 different classes that change the way you strategize and interact with dungeons.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Manage your resources: time, money, and health.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Full narration and impeccable soundtrack.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Quick and accessible dungeon crawls allow for a dungeon before bed or a full night of strategizing.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Roguelike permadeath, procedural dungeon generation, and team synergies to discover.</li></ul><br>Will your party overcome the Lich King's forces and end this ceaseless night?",
